<li>Indjieva, Elena (2009): <a href="http://www.ling.hawaii.edu/graduate/Elena%20Indjieva_Final%20Dissertation.pdf" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Oirat Tobi: Intonational structure of the Oirat language</a>. University of Hawaii. Dissertation.</li>
<li>Janhunen, Juha (ed.) (2003): <i>The Mongolic languages</i>. London: Routledge.</li>
